(101, 'The Holiday', 'Romantic comedy,Holiday,', 'Two women, who each have just endured a horrid breakup with a lover, swap homes for Christmas.', '026', 2006, '2020-10-23T00:00Z', '2020-10-23T03:03Z', '183', 'MV001801350000', '162526', '2006-12-05', 'en', 'Two women, one (Cameron Diaz) from America and one (Kate Winslet) from Britain, swap homes at Christmastime after bad breakups with their boyfriends. Each woman finds romance with a local man (Jude Law, Jack Black) but realizes that the imminent return home may end the relationship.', '10918'),
