(201, 'Lean on Pete', 'Drama,', 'A teen embarks on an odyssey across the new American frontier to save a racehorse from slaughter.', '571', 2017, '2020-10-23T02:00Z', '2020-10-23T04:05Z', '125', 'MV010615880000', '14841156', '2017-09-01', 'en-GB', 'Charley, a teen living with his single father, finds work caring for an aging racehorse named Lean on Pete. When he learns Pete is bound for slaughter, the two embark on an odyssey across the new American frontier in search of a place to call home.', '11160'),
(202, 'Man on Fire', 'Crime drama,', 'A bodyguard (Denzel Washington) takes revenge on a girl\'s (Dakota Fanning) kidnappers.', '069', 2004, '2020-10-23T02:00Z', '2020-10-23T05:00Z', '180', 'MV001481500000', '34417', '2004-04-21', 'en', 'In a Mexico City wracked by a recent wave of kidnappings, ex-CIA operative John Creasy (Denzel Washington) reluctantly accepts a job as a bodyguard for 9-year-old Lupita (Dakota Fanning), the daughter of wealthy businessman Samuel Ramos (Marc Anthony). Just as Creasy begins to develop a fondness for the young girl, a bloodthirsty gunman (Jesús Ochoa) kidnaps her. Now, Creasy must pick off a succession of corrupt cops and criminals to reach his ultimate object of vengeance.', '11163'),
