(218, 'Delta Force 2: The Columbian Connection', 'Action,', 'Colonel (Chuck Norris) leads raid on Latin thug\'s (Billy Drago) cocaine cartel.', '622', 1990, '2020-10-23T02:13Z', '2020-10-23T04:08Z', '115', 'MV008200070000', '12491', '1990', 'en', 'Ruthless Colombian drug lord Ramon Cota (Billy Drago) is tightening his hold on the global cocaine trade. With the Drug Enforcement Administration unsuccessful in blocking the steady stream of narcotics from entering the United States, the U.S. Army\'s Delta Force is enlisted to try and bring Cota to justice. But when Cota strikes at Maj. Bobby Chavez\'s (Paul Perri) family, the mission suddenly becomes very personal for Col. Scott McCoy (Chuck Norris).', '49767'),
(219, 'The Art of Racing in the Rain', 'Comedy drama,', 'A race car driver develops a special bond with a dog that wants to be reincarnated into a human.', '514', 2019, '2020-10-23T02:15Z', '2020-10-23T04:05Z', '110', 'MV012215130000', '16391044', '2019-08-09', 'en', 'Denny Swift is a Formula One race car driver who understands that the techniques needed on the racetrack can also be used to successfully navigate everyday life. Besides his career, Denny has three loves of his life -- his beautiful wife, their young daughter and his best friend -- a dog who wants to be reincarnated into a human.', '16585'),
(220, 'Traición', 'Crime drama,Romance,', 'Félix y Misela, padre e hija, deben traicionarse el uno al otro para poder continuar con sus vidas.', '982', 2018, '2020-10-23T02:15Z', '2020-10-23T03:42Z', '87', 'MV013420090000', '17619489', '2018', 'es', 'Una historia que narra la tormentosa relación entre un padre y su hija, quienes deben traicionarse el uno al otro para poder continuar con sus vidas.', '52208'),
(221, 'Stan & Ollie', 'Biography,Comedy drama,Historical drama,', 'Comedy duo Stan Laurel and Oliver Hardy face an uncertain future as they perform live shows in 1953.', '609', 2018, '2020-10-23T02:19Z', '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '101', 'MV012002580000', '16108758', '2018-10-21', 'en', 'Laurel and Hardy -- the world\'s greatest comedy team -- face an uncertain future as their golden era of Hollywood films remain long behind them. Diminished by age, the duo set out to reconnect with their adoring fans by touring variety halls in Britain in 1953. The shows become an instant hit, but Stan and Ollie can\'t quite shake the past as long-buried tension and Oliver\'s failing health start to threaten their precious partnership.', '17125'),
(222, 'I Love You Phillip Morris', 'Romantic comedy,Drama,', 'A con man (Jim Carrey) meets the love (Ewan McGregor) of his life behind bars.', '540', 2009, '2020-10-23T02:20Z', '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '100', 'MV002576660000', '3595211', '2009-01-19', 'en', 'Steven Russell (Jim Carrey) becomes a cop, gets married and starts a family, but after a terrible car accident, he vows to be true to himself. He comes out of the closet, moves to Florida, and finances a luxurious lifestyle with bad checks and credit cards. In prison, Steven meets Phillip (Ewan McGregor), a mild-mannered inmate who becomes the love of his life. Determined to build a beautiful life with his lover, Steven embarks on another crime spree.', '16620'),
(223, 'The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn Part 2', 'Romance,Fantasy,', 'The Cullens seek help from allies all over the world to protect Renesmee from the Volturi.', '038', 2012, '2020-10-23T02:25Z', '2020-10-23T05:00Z', '155', 'MV003820570000', '8992284', '2012-11-16', 'en', 'Bella (Kristen Stewart) awakes -- as a vampire -- from her life-threatening labor, and her newborn daughter, Renesmee, proves to be very special indeed. While Bella adjusts to her new state of being, Renesmee experiences accelerated growth. When the Volturi learn of the baby\'s existence, they declare her to be an abomination and sentence the Cullens to death. Bella, Edward (Robert Pattinson) and the rest of the clan seek help from allies around the world to protect their family.', '10986'),
