(225, 'Hedwig and the Angry Inch', 'Musical,', 'A rock singer (John Cameron Mitchell) sues her protege (Michael Pitt) for plagiarism.', '513', 2001, '2020-10-23T02:30Z', '2020-10-23T04:05Z', '95', 'MV001055710000', '27370', '2001-07-20', 'en', 'A German emigrant living in a trailer in Kansas is the victim of a botched sex-change operation. Adapted from the critically acclaimed off-Broadway rock theater hit, \"Hedwig and the Angry Inch\" tells the story of the \"internationally ignored\" rock singer, Hedwig, and her search for stardom and love.', '10243'),
(226, 'Austin Powers in Goldmember', 'Comedy,', 'Austin (Mike Myers) goes back to 1975 to rescue his captive father.', '050', 2002, '2020-10-23T02:30Z', '2020-10-23T04:30Z', '120', 'MV001231310000', '30078', '2002-07-26', 'en', 'Teaming up with the mysterious yet peculiar Goldmember, Dr. Evil hatches a time-traveling scheme to take over the world, one that involves the kidnapping of Nigel Powers, Austin\'s beloved father and England\'s most renowned spy. As he chases the villains through time, Austin visits 1975 and joins forces with his old flame, Foxxy Cleopatra, a streetwise but stylish detective. Together Austin and Foxxy must find a way to save Nigel and stop Dr. Evil and Goldmember from their mischievous mayhem.', '11218'),
