(229, 'Love Is Strange', 'Drama,', 'A recently married gay couple must move into separate households after losing their home.', '621', 2014, '2020-10-23T02:35Z', '2020-10-23T04:14Z', '99', 'MV005675610000', '10705131', '2014-08-22', 'en', 'A recently married gay couple (John Lithgow, Alfred Molina) are forced to move into separate households after they lose their home.', '49751'),
(230, 'Showtime', 'Comedy,Action,', 'Two cops (Robert De Niro, Eddie Murphy) work on a reality-based TV show.', '604', 2002, '2020-10-23T02:41Z', '2020-10-23T04:19Z', '98', 'MV001177460000', '29226', '2002-03-15', 'en', 'When a no-nonsense LAPD detective (Robert De Niro) is forced to star in a reality-based television show with a frustrated actor-turned-LAPD-patrolman (Eddie Murphy), they find their lives turned upside down by a powerhouse producer (Rene Russo) and her very intrusive camera crew.', '14870'),
(231, 'Killer Elite', 'Action,Thriller,', 'A special-ops agent (Jason Statham) returns from self-imposed exile to rescue his kidnapped mentor.', '582', 2011, '2020-10-23T02:41Z', '2020-10-23T04:40Z', '119', 'MV003630160000', '8712034', '2011-09-23', 'en', 'Danny Bryce (Jason Statham), one of the world\'s deadliest special-ops agents, returns from self-imposed exile after his mentor, Hunter (Robert De Niro) is captured. Danny reassembles his former team of skilled commandos to launch a rescue mission, and also to infiltrate the highly feared military unit, the British Special Air Service. The mission will not be easy, for Danny and his team must cut their way through Spike (Clive Owen) and a team of assassins known as the Feather Men.', '16311'),
(232, 'King Arthur: Legend of the Sword', 'Adventure,Action,Fantasy,', 'Robbed of his birthright, Arthur embraces his destiny after pulling the Excalibur sword from stone.', '532', 2017, '2020-10-23T02:45Z', '2020-10-23T04:55Z', '130', 'MV008331720000', '12394972', '2017-05-12', 'en', 'After the murder of his father, young Arthur\'s power-hungry uncle Vortigern seizes control of the crown. Robbed of his birthright, he grows up the hard way in the back alleys of the city, not knowing who he truly is. When fate leads him to pull the Excalibur sword from stone, Arthur embraces his true destiny to become a legendary fighter and leader.', '10121'),
(233, 'Hour of the Gun', 'Western,Drama,', 'Wyatt Earp (James Garner), Doc Holliday (Jason Robards) and posse hunt Clanton gang.', '640', 1967, '2020-10-23T02:45Z', '2020-10-23T04:30Z', '105', 'MV000023780000', '1481', '1967-10-10', 'en', 'While the Earp brothers may have won the gunfight at the O.K. Corral, they didn\'t escape unscathed for long. Seeking revenge over their fallen comrades, members of the Clanton gang go after the Earp family, gunning down both Virgil and Morgan Earp. But they don\'t succeed at getting Wyatt (James Garner). Now it\'s his turn to seek revenge. With Doc Holliday (Jason Robards) by his side, Wyatt forms a posse, and they won\'t rest until every member of the Clanton gang is dead.', '33668'),
(234, 'Point Break', 'Action,Thriller,', 'An FBI man (Keanu Reeves) turns surfer to nab rubber-masked bank robbers.', '523', 1991, '2020-10-23T02:55Z', '2020-10-23T05:00Z', '125', 'MV000337110000', '13324', '1991-07-12', 'en', 'After a string of bizarre bank robberies in Southern California, with the crooks donning masks of various former presidents, a federal agent, Johnny Utah (Keanu Reeves), infiltrates the suspected gang. But this is no ordinary group of robbers. They\'re surfers -- led by the charismatic Bodhi (Patrick Swayze) -- who are addicted to the rush of thievery. But when Utah falls in love with a female surfer, Tyler (Lori Petty), who is close to the gang, it complicates his sense of duty.', '18432'),
(235, 'En carne propia', 'Drama,', 'Un periodista, que toma sus casos a la ligera, vive en carne propia una de sus noticias.', '980', 1959, '2020-10-23T02:55Z', '2020-10-23T04:30Z', '95', 'MV001111570000', '73636', '1959', 'es', 'Un periodista, que toma sus casos a la ligera, cambia de parecer cuando vive en carne propia una de sus noticias.', '35401'),
(236, 'Hellboy', 'Action,Adventure,Fantasy,', 'Legendary half-demon Hellboy battles an ancient sorceress who\'s out to avenge a past betrayal.', '542', 2019, '2020-10-23T02:58Z', '2020-10-23T05:00Z', '122', 'MV010623280000', '14852067', '2019-04-12', 'en', 'While battling a trio of rampaging giants, the legendary half-demon Hellboy encounters Nimue the Blood Queen, an ancient resurrected sorceress who\'s out to avenge a past betrayal. Suddenly caught in a clash between the supernatural and the human, Hellboy soon becomes hell-bent on stopping Nimue without triggering the end of the world.', '18436'),
(237, '28 Days Later', 'Horror,Science fiction,', 'Survivors (Cillian Murphy, Noah Huntley, Naomie Harris) evade virus-infected humans in London.', '058', 2002, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T05:30Z', '150', 'MV001294740000', '31044', '2002-11-01', 'en', 'A group of misguided animal rights activists free a caged chimp infected with the \"Rage\" virus from a medical research lab. When London bike courier Jim (Cillian Murphy) wakes up from a coma a month after, he finds his city all but deserted. On the run from the zombie-like victims of the Rage, Jim stumbles upon a group of survivors, including Selena (Naomie Harris) and cab driver Frank (Brendan Gleeson), and joins them on a perilous journey to what he hopes will be safety.', '11097'),
(238, '28 Days Later', 'Horror,Science fiction,', 'Survivors (Cillian Murphy, Noah Huntley, Naomie Harris) evade virus-infected humans in London.', '111', 2002, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T05:30Z', '150', 'MV001294740000', '31044', '2002-11-01', 'en', 'A group of misguided animal rights activists free a caged chimp infected with the \"Rage\" virus from a medical research lab. When London bike courier Jim (Cillian Murphy) wakes up from a coma a month after, he finds his city all but deserted. On the run from the zombie-like victims of the Rage, Jim stumbles upon a group of survivors, including Selena (Naomie Harris) and cab driver Frank (Brendan Gleeson), and joins them on a perilous journey to what he hopes will be safety.', '11097'),
(239, 'The Meddler', 'Comedy drama,', 'After the death of her husband, a woman moves to Los Angeles to be closer to her daughter.', '585', 2015, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T04:48Z', '108', 'MV008228230000', '12313854', '2015-09-14', 'en', 'After the death of her husband, a woman (Susan Sarandon) moves from New Jersey to Los Angeles to be closer to her daughter (Rose Byrne).', '19634'),
(240, 'The Warriors', 'Action,', 'Framed, members of a Coney Island street gang wage a desperate battle to reach their home turf.', '539', 1979, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T04:35Z', '95', 'MV005888780000', '4866', '1979', 'en', 'A turf battle between New York City street gangs that rages from Coney Island to the Bronx. The Warriors are mistakenly fingered for the killing of a gang leader. Soon they have every gang in the city out to get revenge and they must make their way across the city to their own turf.', '12508'),
(241, 'The Break-Up', 'Romantic comedy,', 'A couple (Vince Vaughn, Jennifer Aniston) end their relationship, but neither is willing to move.', '062', 2006, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T05:00Z', '120', 'MV001689700000', '159819', '2006-06-02', 'en', 'When Brooke (Jennifer Aniston), an art dealer, and Gary (Vince Vaughn), a tour-bus driver, finally call it quits in their relationship, neither is willing to move out of their shared condo. With their friends suggesting a series of underhanded tactics that fail to get either Brooke or Gary to cave in, the only solution is to become hostile roommates.', '10057'),
(242, 'The Break-Up', 'Romantic comedy,', 'A couple (Vince Vaughn, Jennifer Aniston) end their relationship, but neither is willing to move.', '167', 2006, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T05:00Z', '120', 'MV001689700000', '159819', '2006-06-02', 'en', 'When Brooke (Jennifer Aniston), an art dealer, and Gary (Vince Vaughn), a tour-bus driver, finally call it quits in their relationship, neither is willing to move out of their shared condo. With their friends suggesting a series of underhanded tactics that fail to get either Brooke or Gary to cave in, the only solution is to become hostile roommates.', '10057'),
(243, 'La odisea de los giles', 'Adventure,Comedy,', 'Un grupo de vecinos descubre que perdieron todos sus ahorros debido a una estafa.', '524', 2019, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T04:55Z', '115', 'MV012687200000', '17011913', '2019-11-29', 'es', 'Cuando un grupo de vecinos descubre que perdieron todos los ahorros que tenían debido a una estafa realizada por un abogado y el gerente de un banco, se organizan y arman un plan para recuperar lo que les pertenece.', '24575'),
(244, 'Hope Floats', 'Romance,', 'A newly divorced woman (Sandra Bullock) finds love in her hometown.', '070', 1998, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '180', 'MV000587630000', '21031', '1998-05-29', 'en', 'Birdee Pruitt (Sandra Bullock) has been humiliated on live television by her best friend, Connie (Rosanna Arquette), who\'s been sleeping with Birdee\'s husband, Bill (Michael Paré). Birdee tries starting over with her daughter, Bernice (Mae Whitman), by returning to her small Texas hometown, but she\'s faced with petty old acquaintances who are thrilled to see Birdee unhappy -- except for her friend Justin (Harry Connick Jr.). As he helps Birdee get back on her feet, love begins to blossom.', '10138'),
(245, 'Hope Floats', 'Romance,', 'A newly divorced woman (Sandra Bullock) finds love in her hometown.', '293', 1998, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '180', 'MV000587630000', '21031', '1998-05-29', 'en', 'Birdee Pruitt (Sandra Bullock) has been humiliated on live television by her best friend, Connie (Rosanna Arquette), who\'s been sleeping with Birdee\'s husband, Bill (Michael Paré). Birdee tries starting over with her daughter, Bernice (Mae Whitman), by returning to her small Texas hometown, but she\'s faced with petty old acquaintances who are thrilled to see Birdee unhappy -- except for her friend Justin (Harry Connick Jr.). As he helps Birdee get back on her feet, love begins to blossom.', '10138'),
(246, 'Downhill', 'Comedy drama,', 'A man lands in hot water after he runs away from an avalanche, leaving behind his wife and two sons.', '520', 2020, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T04:30Z', '90', 'MV013520890000', '17669185', '2020-01-26', 'en', 'A woman starts to have second doubts about her husband after he runs away from an approaching avalanche, leaving her and their two sons behind.', '16576'),
(247, 'The Art of Getting By', 'Comedy drama,', 'A disaffected teenager (Freddie Highmore) meets a kindred spirit (Emma Roberts).', '522', 2011, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T04:25Z', '85', 'MV003513240000', '8555502', '2011-01-23', 'en', 'George (Freddie Highmore) is a senior at a posh Manhattan prep school, but his disaffected attitude leaves little room for toeing the line. He\'d rather doodle and read philosophy, and he strenuously avoids his parents (Rita Wilson, Sam Robards) whenever possible. Unfortunately, George\'s attitude is endangering his chances of graduating. Then he meets Sally (Emma Roberts). George finds himself falling in love with her, but an older artist (Michael Angarano) adds a complication to the mix.', '18430');
INSERT INTO `tv_movies` (`id`, `title`, `genres`, `description`, `channel`, `release_year`, `startTime`, `endTime`, `duration`, `tmsId`, `rootId`, `releaseDate`, `titleLang`, `longDescription`, `stationId`) VALUES
(248, 'Mary Shelley\'s Frankenstein', 'Horror,', 'Dr. Frankenstein (Kenneth Branagh) creates soulless monster (Robert De Niro).', '596', 1994, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T05:05Z', '125', 'MV000407490000', '16144', '1994-11-04', 'en', 'As Viktor Frankenstein (Kenneth Branagh) is dying he shares a tale of gruesome terror with a sea captain. Viktor, using previous experiments by a brilliant scientist, was able to bring a creature (Robert De Niro) assembled from body parts back to life. Once he realized how destructive his experiments had become, he abandoned the creature and tried to live a normal life with his fiance (Helena Bonham Carter). The lonely creature seeks out Viktor and demands one of two things: a bride or revenge.', '66073'),
(249, 'Las calenturas de un fantasma', 'Comedy,', '\"Las sexorcistas\" son tres exuberantes mujeres que tratan de capturar a un fantasmita.', '971', 2018, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T04:50Z', '110', 'MV011619580000', '15568401', '2018', 'es', '\"Las sexorcistas\" son tres exuberantes mujeres que van con su tarot tratando de descubrir y si se puede capturar al fantasmita que todas las noches se aparece en una casa abandonada.', '62401'),
(250, 'My Other Mother', 'Drama,', 'Adopted as a child, a woman reconnects with her mother and extended family at her father\'s funeral.', '185', 2014, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T05:00Z', '120', 'MV006208070000', '11035102', '2014-09-21', 'en', 'Adopted as a child, an anchorwoman (Essence Atkins) reconnects with her birth mother (Lynn Whitfield) and extended family when she attends the funeral of her father.', '76126'),
(251, 'Boyz N the Hood', 'Drama,', 'Three boys become men, one guided by his father, in their racially divided Los Angeles neighborhood.', '597', 1991, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T04:55Z', '115', 'MV000333990000', '13227', '1991-07-12', 'en', 'Tre (Cuba Gooding Jr.) is sent to live with his father, Furious Styles (Larry Fishburne), in tough South Central Los Angeles. Although his hard-nosed father instills proper values and respect in him, and his devout girlfriend Brandi (Nia Long) teaches him about faith, Tre\'s friends Doughboy (Ice Cube) and Ricky (Morris Chestnut) don\'t have the same kind of support and are drawn into the neighborhood\'s booming drug and gang culture, with increasingly tragic results.', '73075'),
(252, 'El colmillo de Buda', 'Adventure,', 'Un hombre inglés posee en su colección el colmillo de buda.', '841', 1949, '2020-10-23T03:00Z', '2020-10-23T05:00Z', '120', 'MV001344640000', '80730', '1949', 'es', 'Un hombre inglés posee en su colección el colmillo de buda y una secta quiere rescatarlo y mata a su sirviente.', '91060'),
(253, 'Where the Heart Is', 'Comedy drama,', 'A pregnant teen (Natalie Portman) is abandoned at an Oklahoma Wal-Mart.', '026', 2000, '2020-10-23T03:03Z', '2020-10-23T04:59Z', '116', 'MV000874120000', '25129', '2000-04-28', 'en', 'After Tennessee teen Novalee Nation (Natalie Portman) is left literally barefoot and pregnant in a Wal-Mart parking lot by her no-good boyfriend, Willy Jack Pickens (Dylan Bruno), she manages to live within the mammoth megastore until her baby\'s abrupt arrival makes her a media darling. After this, Good Samaritan nurse Lexie (Ashley Judd) takes in Novalee and her newborn daughter. Before long, Lexie and Novalee form a life-changing bond of friendship and sisterhood.', '10918'),
(254, 'Where the Heart Is', 'Comedy drama,', 'A pregnant teen (Natalie Portman) is abandoned at an Oklahoma Wal-Mart.', '170', 2000, '2020-10-23T03:03Z', '2020-10-23T04:59Z', '116', 'MV000874120000', '25129', '2000-04-28', 'en', 'After Tennessee teen Novalee Nation (Natalie Portman) is left literally barefoot and pregnant in a Wal-Mart parking lot by her no-good boyfriend, Willy Jack Pickens (Dylan Bruno), she manages to live within the mammoth megastore until her baby\'s abrupt arrival makes her a media darling. After this, Good Samaritan nurse Lexie (Ashley Judd) takes in Novalee and her newborn daughter. Before long, Lexie and Novalee form a life-changing bond of friendship and sisterhood.', '10918'),
(255, 'True Grit', 'Western,', 'A marshal (John Wayne) helps a girl (Kim Darby) find her father\'s killer.', '607', 1969, '2020-10-23T03:10Z', '2020-10-23T05:22Z', '132', 'MV000075410000', '4436', '1969-06-11', 'en', 'After hired hand Tom Chaney (Jeff Corey) murders the father of 14-year-old Mattie Ross (Kim Darby), she seeks vengeance and hires U.S. Marshal \"Rooster\" Cogburn (John Wayne), a man of \"true grit,\" to track Chaney into Indian territory. As the two begin their pursuit, a Texas Ranger, La Boeuf (Glen Campbell), joins the manhunt in hopes of capturing Chaney for the murder of a Texas senator and collecting a substantial reward. The three clash on their quest of bringing to justice the same man.', '102906'),
(256, 'Safe House', 'Action,Thriller,', 'A rookie and a renegade agent try to stay alive while trying to determine who\'s trying to kill them.', '537', 2012, '2020-10-23T03:15Z', '2020-10-23T05:11Z', '116', 'MV003685510000', '8786328', '2012-02-10', 'en', 'For the past year, rookie CIA agent Matt Weston (Ryan Reynolds) has been eager to prove himself while cooling his heels at an inactive South African post. He gets the chance when Tobin Frost (Denzel Washington), a turncoat operative, is brought to Weston\'s safe house for debriefing. But soon after Frost\'s arrival, mercenaries attack, and Weston and Frost barely escape with their lives. The two men must join forces and try to stay alive long enough to figure out who wants them dead.', '25620'),
(257, 'Nurse 3D', 'Thriller,', 'An alluring nurse (Paz de la Huerta) lures cheating men to their deaths.', '599', 2014, '2020-10-23T03:15Z', '2020-10-23T04:40Z', '85', 'MV005260800000', '10326521', '2014-02-07', 'en', 'A young nurse (Katrina Bowden) begins to suspect that a sexy colleague (Paz de la Huerta) is responsible for murdering a string of unfaithful men.', '68409'),
(258, 'Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales', 'Adventure,Action,Fantasy,', 'Deadly ghost sailors pursue Jack Sparrow as he searches for the legendary Trident of Poseidon.', '067', 2017, '2020-10-23T03:15Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '165', 'MV010417590000', '12009531', '2017', 'en', 'Thrust into an all-new adventure, a down-on-his-luck Capt. Jack Sparrow feels the winds of ill-fortune blowing even more strongly when deadly ghost sailors led by his old nemesis, the evil Capt. Salazar, escape from the Devil\'s Triangle. Jack\'s only hope of survival lies in seeking out the legendary Trident of Poseidon, but to find it, he must forge an uneasy alliance with a brilliant and beautiful astronomer and a headstrong young man in the British navy.', '11164'),
(259, 'Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales', 'Adventure,Action,Fantasy,', 'Deadly ghost sailors pursue Jack Sparrow as he searches for the legendary Trident of Poseidon.', '103', 2017, '2020-10-23T03:15Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '165', 'MV010417590000', '12009531', '2017', 'en', 'Thrust into an all-new adventure, a down-on-his-luck Capt. Jack Sparrow feels the winds of ill-fortune blowing even more strongly when deadly ghost sailors led by his old nemesis, the evil Capt. Salazar, escape from the Devil\'s Triangle. Jack\'s only hope of survival lies in seeking out the legendary Trident of Poseidon, but to find it, he must forge an uneasy alliance with a brilliant and beautiful astronomer and a headstrong young man in the British navy.', '11164'),
(260, 'Truth', 'Drama,', 'Controversy surrounds CBS anchor Dan Rather and \"60 Minutes\" producer Mary Mapes (Cate Blanchett).', '602', 2015, '2020-10-23T03:17Z', '2020-10-23T05:26Z', '129', 'MV007897960000', '12009105', '2015-09-12', 'en', 'Controversy surrounds CBS anchor Dan Rather (Robert Redford) and \"60 Minutes\" producer Mary Mapes (Cate Blanchett) after the network broadcasts a report about President George W. Bush and his military service.', '10178'),
(261, 'My Super Ex-Girlfriend', 'Romantic comedy,', 'A superheroine (Uma Thurman) takes revenge after her boyfriend breaks up with her.', '541', 2006, '2020-10-23T03:20Z', '2020-10-23T05:00Z', '100', 'MV001776850000', '160887', '2006-07-21', 'en', 'A young man (Luke Wilson) discovers that the beautiful but manipulative woman (Uma Thurman) he is dating is really a superheroine known as G-Girl. After breaking up with her, he learns that \"hell hath no fury like a woman scorned\" as she unleashes her considerable powers against him.', '18434'),
(262, 'Ice Age', 'Comedy,Adventure,Animated,Children,', 'Ice Age animals (Ray Romano, John Alberto Leguizamo, Denis Leary) find and travel with a human baby.', '608', 2002, '2020-10-23T03:20Z', '2020-10-23T04:43Z', '83', 'MV001203820000', '29626', '2002-03-15', 'en', 'Twenty-thousand years ago, Earth is a wondrous, prehistoric world filled with great danger, not the least of which is the beginning of the Ice Age. To avoid a really bad frostbite, the planet\'s majestic creatures - and a few small, slothful ones - begin migrating south . The story revolves around sub-zero heroes: a woolly mammoth, a saber-toothed tiger, a sloth and a prehistoric combination of a squirrel and rat, known as Scrat.', '102903'),
(263, 'Hotel Transylvania', 'Comedy,Fantasy,Animated,Children,', 'Dracula invites the world\'s most-infamous monsters to celebrate his daughter\'s 118th birthday.', '581', 2012, '2020-10-23T03:21Z', '2020-10-23T04:58Z', '97', 'MV003904140000', '9128632', '2012-09-28', 'en', 'When monsters want to get away from it all, they go to Count Dracula\'s (Adam Sandler) Hotel Transylvania, a lavish resort where they can be themselves without humans around to bother them. On one special weekend, Dracula invites creatures like the Invisible Man, the Mummy and others to celebrate the 118th birthday of his daughter, Mavis (Selena Gomez). However, an unforeseen complication unfolds when an ordinary human unwittingly crashes the party and falls in love with Mavis.', '12719'),
(264, 'Mystery of the Wax Museum', 'Horror,', 'Mad curator (Lionel Atwill) of wax museum sees his next Marie Antoinette (Fay Wray).', '064', 1933, '2020-10-23T03:30Z', '2020-10-23T05:00Z', '90', 'MV000051760000', '3130', '1933-09-01', 'en', 'Ivan Igor (Lionel Atwill) is the sculptor at a famous wax museum in London. When his partner, Joe Worth (Edwin Maxwell), burns down the museum for the insurance money, Igor is trapped inside. Years later he re-emerges in New York as the curator of a new wax museum, which boasts incredibly lifelike statues. When model Joan Gale (Monica Bannister) goes missing, however, reporter Florence Dempsey (Glenda Farrell) follows the clues to Igor\'s museum, where she discovers a terrible secret.', '12852'),
(265, 'Mystery of the Wax Museum', 'Horror,', 'Mad curator (Lionel Atwill) of wax museum sees his next Marie Antoinette (Fay Wray).', '631', 1933, '2020-10-23T03:30Z', '2020-10-23T05:00Z', '90', 'MV000051760000', '3130', '1933-09-01', 'en', 'Ivan Igor (Lionel Atwill) is the sculptor at a famous wax museum in London. When his partner, Joe Worth (Edwin Maxwell), burns down the museum for the insurance money, Igor is trapped inside. Years later he re-emerges in New York as the curator of a new wax museum, which boasts incredibly lifelike statues. When model Joan Gale (Monica Bannister) goes missing, however, reporter Florence Dempsey (Glenda Farrell) follows the clues to Igor\'s museum, where she discovers a terrible secret.', '12852'),
(266, 'Face/Off', 'Action,', 'An FBI agent (John Travolta) and his nemesis (Nicolas Cage) trade physical identities.', '553', 1997, '2020-10-23T03:30Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '150', 'MV000510170000', '19525', '1997-06-27', 'en', 'Obsessed with bringing terrorist Castor Troy (Nicolas Cage) to justice, FBI agent Sean Archer (John Travolta) tracks down Troy, who has boarded a plane in Los Angeles. After the plane crashes and Troy is severely injured, possibly dead, Archer undergoes surgery to remove his face and replace it with Troy\'s. As Archer tries to use his disguise to elicit information about a bomb from Troy\'s brother, Troy awakes from a coma and forces the doctor who performed the surgery to give him Archer\'s face.', '16153'),
(267, 'I\'ll Sleep When I\'m Dead', 'Crime drama,Thriller,', 'A man (Clive Owen) seeks revenge against his brother\'s (Jonathan Rhys-Meyers) killer.', '572', 2003, '2020-10-23T03:30Z', '2020-10-23T05:15Z', '105', 'MV001493340000', '34637', '2003-05-16', 'en', 'Former gangster Will Graham (Clive Owen) is living a quiet life in the English countryside. When he learns his brother (Jonathan Rhys-Meyers), a low-level drug dealer, has committed suicide, Will travels to London to investigate his death. He reconnects with his former lover, Helen (Charlotte Rampling), and starts piecing together the circumstances surrounding his brother\'s death. When he learns a man named Boad (Malcolm McDowell) is responsible, Will seeks revenge.', '17663'),
(268, 'The Harder They Come', 'Drama,', 'A poor Jamaican (Jimmy Cliff) comes to Kingston, cuts a record and becomes an outlaw folk hero.', '623', 1972, '2020-10-23T03:30Z', '2020-10-23T05:15Z', '105', 'MV000122400000', '6403', '1972', 'en', 'Ivanhoe Martin (Jimmy Cliff) arrives in Kingston, Jamaica, looking for work and, after some initial struggles, lands a recording contract as a reggae singer. He records his first song, \"The Harder They Come,\" but after a bitter dispute with a manipulative producer named Hilton (Bob Charlton), soon finds himself resorting to petty crime in order to pay the bills. He deals marijuana, kills some abusive cops and earns local folk hero status. Meanwhile, his record is topping the charts.', '10201'),
(269, 'Hotel Rwanda', 'Drama,', 'A hotelier (Don Cheadle) saves 1,200 Tutsi refugees from slaughter.', '633', 2004, '2020-10-23T03:30Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '150', 'MV001530430000', '35240', '2004-12-22', 'en', 'Paul Rusesabagina (Don Cheadle), a Hutu, manages the Hôtel des Mille Collines and lives a happy life with his Tutsi wife (Sophie Okonedo) and their three children. But when Hutu military forces initiate a campaign of ethnic cleansing against the Tutsi minority, Paul is compelled to allow refugees to take shelter in his hotel. As the U.N. pulls out, Paul must struggle alone to protect the Tutsi refugees in the face of the escalating violence later known as the Rwandan genocide.', '58530'),
(270, 'Walk of Shame', 'Comedy,', 'An ill-advised tryst leaves a woman stranded in downtown L.A. just hours before a job interview.', '534', 2014, '2020-10-23T03:33Z', '2020-10-23T05:09Z', '96', 'MV004798460000', '9915745', '2014-05-02', 'en', 'Meghan (Elizabeth Banks) is an aspiring news anchor in the cutthroat world of Los Angeles television. After an audition for her dream job ends in failure, she goes out for an uncharacteristic night of partying. The next morning, she awakes in a stranger\'s bed and hears a phone message from her agent telling her the job is hers if she can make it across town by 5:00 pm. Stranded in an unknown area without money, phone or transportation, she races to the most important interview of her life.', '18435'),
(271, 'QTH', 'Drama,War,', 'Un suboficial, un cabo y dos marinos tienen que controlar la entrada estratégica de un canal.', '984', 2016, '2020-10-23T03:35Z', '2020-10-23T05:20Z', '105', 'MV010734610000', '14991880', '2016', 'es', 'En el Canal Beagle, un suboficial, un cabo y dos marinos tienen la misión de cuidar y controlar la entrada estratégica del canal. Ellos viven una experiencia de guerra con la amenaza de invasión inglesa hasta llegar a una situación extrema.', '79680'),
(272, 'Mi pueblo', 'Action,', 'Un mantense, quien emigró a los EE. UU., regresa a su ciudad y la encuentra plagada de injusticias.', '983', 2014, '2020-10-23T03:35Z', '2020-10-23T05:25Z', '110', 'MV009703820000', '13675675', '2014', 'es', 'Adrián González es un mantense que decide emigrar hacia los Estados Unidos para darle una vida mejor a su familia. Pero a su regreso encuentra una ciudad plagada de injusticias, en donde familias enteras son despojadas de sus tierras.', '79692'),
(273, 'Muñecos infernales', 'Horror,', 'Tres jóvenes roban un ídolo que encierra una maldición y se lo llevan a unos especialistas.', '985', 1960, '2020-10-23T03:35Z', '2020-10-23T05:05Z', '90', 'MV013886680000', '45109', '1960', 'es', 'Tres jóvenes roban un ídolo en Haití que encierra una maldición. Luego, se lo muestran a unos especialistas en ciencias ocultas que ya conocen la historia del objeto y los secretos que esconde.', '79695'),
(274, 'The Great Gilly Hopkins', 'Comedy drama,', 'A young girl devises a scheme to escape from her new foster home and reunite with her birth mother.', '521', 2016, '2020-10-23T03:38Z', '2020-10-23T05:15Z', '97', 'MV007928790000', '12036558', '2016-10-07', 'en', 'Young and feisty Gilly Hopkins (Sophie Nélisse) devises a scheme to escape from her new foster home and reunite with her birth mother.', '16619'),
(275, 'Gretel & Hansel', 'Horror,Fantasy,', 'A girl and her brother unwittingly stumble upon the house of an evil witch in the dark woods.', '595', 2020, '2020-10-23T03:40Z', '2020-10-23T05:10Z', '90', 'MV012896380000', '17232014', '2020-01-31', 'en', 'When their mother descends into madness, siblings Gretel and Hansel must fend for themselves in the dark and unforgiving woods. Hungry and scared, they fortuitously stumble upon a bounty of food left outside an isolated home. Invited inside by the seemingly friendly owner, the children soon suspect that her generous but mysterious behavior is part of a sinister plan to do them harm.', '65669'),
(276, 'Star Trek: Insurrection', 'Science fiction,Action,', 'Capt. Picard and members of his crew defy Federation orders to save an alien race.', '598', 1998, '2020-10-23T03:40Z', '2020-10-23T05:25Z', '105', 'MV000656260000', '22138', '1998-12-11', 'en', 'A Federation mission to the planet Ba\'ku takes a dangerous turn when a malfunctioning android, Data (Brent Spiner), takes a cultural task force hostage. When Capt. Picard (Patrick Stewart) and his crew investigate, they uncover the truth about the Federation mission: It was actually a systematic ploy by the Son\'a to displace the peaceful inhabitants of Ba\'ku. Now Picard and his crew must thwart the plot even while experiencing strange side effects from exposure to the planet\'s surface.', '74320'),
(277, 'La palabra de Pablo', 'Drama,', 'Pablo inventa mentiras para que su padre crea que su joven novia le es infiel.', '982', 2018, '2020-10-23T03:42Z', '2020-10-23T05:08Z', '86', 'MV011879560000', '15873574', '2018', 'es', 'Pablo es hijo de un abogado asociado a un escándalo de corrupción. Su padre tiene una novia joven que incomoda a Pablo, lo que le conduce a una serie de mentiras para convencer a su progenitor de que la mujer le es infiel con su hijastro.', '52208'),
(278, 'Zoom', 'Comedy,Action,Adventure,Children,', 'A former superhero (Tim Allen) becomes mentor to a ragtag group of young heroes-in-training.', '620', 2006, '2020-10-23T03:43Z', '2020-10-23T05:13Z', '90', 'MV001777970000', '159751', '2006-08-11', 'en', 'Capt. Zoom, or Jack (Tim Allen), as he is now known, has long since given up his career of fighting evil and protecting the defenseless. The former superhero gets back into the game when he takes a job at a private academy, where he must whip into shape a ragtag group of heroes-in-training.', '15295'),
(279, 'The Hobbit: The Desolation of Smaug', 'Fantasy,Adventure,', 'Bilbo and his companions reach the Lonely Mountain, where they encounter the fearsome dragon Smaug.', '086', 2013, '2020-10-23T03:45Z', '2020-10-23T07:30Z', '225', 'MV012920990000', '9458059', '2013', 'en', 'Having survived the first part of their unsettling journey, Bilbo Baggins (Martin Freeman) and his companions (Ian McKellen, Richard Armitage) continue east. More dangers await them, including the skin-changer Beorn and the giant spiders of Milkwood. After escaping capture by the dangerous Wood Elves, Bilbo and the dwarves journey to Lake-town and, finally, to the Lonely Mountain, where they face the greatest danger of all: the fearsome dragon Smaug (Benedict Cumberbatch).', '18332'),
(280, 'The Hobbit: The Desolation of Smaug', 'Fantasy,Adventure,', 'Bilbo and his companions reach the Lonely Mountain, where they encounter the fearsome dragon Smaug.', '110', 2013, '2020-10-23T03:45Z', '2020-10-23T07:30Z', '225', 'MV012920990000', '9458059', '2013', 'en', 'Having survived the first part of their unsettling journey, Bilbo Baggins (Martin Freeman) and his companions (Ian McKellen, Richard Armitage) continue east. More dangers await them, including the skin-changer Beorn and the giant spiders of Milkwood. After escaping capture by the dangerous Wood Elves, Bilbo and the dwarves journey to Lake-town and, finally, to the Lonely Mountain, where they face the greatest danger of all: the fearsome dragon Smaug (Benedict Cumberbatch).', '18332'),
(281, 'Downton Abbey', 'Drama,', 'The Crawleys and their intrepid staff prepare for a royal visit from the king and queen of England.', '512', 2019, '2020-10-23T03:45Z', '2020-10-23T05:50Z', '125', 'MV012188790000', '16356852', '2019-09-13', 'en', 'The beloved Crawleys and their intrepid staff prepare for the most important moment of their lives. A royal visit from the king and queen of England soon unleashes scandal, romance and intrigue -- leaving the future of Downton hanging in the balance.', '10241'),
(282, 'Contrabando por Amor', 'Drama,', 'Luego de que su padre es asesinado, dos hermanos se independizan.', '890', 1980, '2020-10-23T03:45Z', '2020-10-23T05:25Z', '100', 'MV000229970000', '48903', '1980', 'es', 'Dos hermanos huérfanos deciden separarse, uno se va a los EE.UU. y trabaja como chofer, el otro se queda en México.', '48523'),
(283, 'El señor de la Tahoe', 'Thriller,Western,', 'Un hombre salva al primo y este, agradecido, lo invita a trabajar en su organización.', '972', 2015, '2020-10-23T03:46Z', '2020-10-23T05:27Z', '101', 'MV009722790000', '13704457', '2015', 'es', 'Un hombre descubre que van a asesinar al primo y arriesga su vida para salvarlo, sin importar el precio que debe pagar. El primo, agradecido por tan noble gesto, lo invita a trabajar en su organización.', '44714'),
(284, 'Witness', 'Crime drama,', 'Hunted detective (Harrison Ford) moves in with Amish widow (Kelly McGillis) and her son.', '605', 1985, '2020-10-23T03:47Z', '2020-10-23T05:43Z', '116', 'MV000186450000', '8671', '1985-02-08', 'en', 'After witnessing a brutal murder, young Amish boy Samuel (Lukas Haas) and his mother Rachel (Kelly McGillis) seek protection from police officer John Book (Harrison Ford). When Book uncovers evidence of police corruption involving narcotics lieutenant James McFee (Danny Glover), Book must take Rachel and Samuel, and flee to the Amish countryside where Rachel grew up. There, immersed in Amish culture and tradition, Book and Rachel begin a cautious romance.', '14764'),
(285, 'Michael Clayton', 'Drama,', 'A \"fixer\" (George Clooney) at a corporate law firm faces the biggest challenge of his career.', '516', 2007, '2020-10-23T03:50Z', '2020-10-23T05:50Z', '120', 'MV001897500000', '166244', '2007-10-05', 'en', 'Former prosecutor Michael Clayton (George Clooney) works as a \"fixer\" at the corporate law firm of Kenner, Bach and Ledeen, and takes care of his employer\'s dirty work. Burned out and deep in debt, he is bound tightly to the firm. Clayton faces the biggest challenge of his career when a guilt-ridden attorney (Tom Wilkinson) has a breakdown during a huge class-action lawsuit.', '18431'),
(286, 'Quiéreme porque me muero', 'Comedy,', 'Un empleado se enamora de la sobrina del dueño, porque cree que pronto morirá.', '979', 1953, '2020-10-23T03:50Z', '2020-10-23T05:40Z', '110', 'MV001356540000', '81049', '1953', 'es', 'Un empleado se enamora de la sobrina del dueño, y cree que pronto morirá porque confundieron sus estudios clínicos.', '33628'),
(287, 'Dead Man Down', 'Crime drama,Thriller,', 'Un deseo mutuo de venganza reúne a dos desconocidos a lo largo de un enorme caos.', '973', 2013, '2020-10-23T03:50Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '130', 'MV004307360000', '9512762', '2013-03-08', 'en', 'El pandillero Victor se infiltra en el imperio criminal dirigido por Alphonse, pero su objetivo no es acumular y poder. En su lugar, la misión de Victor es hacer que Alphonse pague por destruir su alguna vez feliz vida. Las maquinaciones de Victor no han pasado desapercibidas; Beatrice, su vecina, observa y espera. Cuando ella descubre el secreto de Victor, ella amenaza con exponerlo a menos que le ayude con su propia campaña de venganza.', '76408'),
(288, 'Highway 301', 'Crime drama,', 'The Tri-State Gang pulls off a string of robberies before being caught by the police.', '1248', 1951, '2020-10-23T03:50Z', '2020-10-23T05:40Z', '110', 'MV000401240000', '58000', '1951', 'en', 'A network of armed robbers successfully gets away with several million dollars before the law can stop them.', '59218'),
(289, 'American Gangster', 'Crime drama,Biography,', 'A chauffeur (Denzel Washington) rises to prominence as the most-powerful crime boss in 1970s Harlem.', '583', 2007, '2020-10-23T03:52Z', '2020-10-23T06:33Z', '161', 'MV001957140000', '159405', '2007-11-02', 'en', 'Frank Lucas (Denzel Washington) earns his living as a chauffeur to one of Harlem\'s leading mobsters. After his boss dies, Frank uses his own ingenuity and strict business code to become one of the inner city\'s most powerful crime bosses. Meanwhile, veteran cop Richie Roberts (Russell Crowe) senses a change in the mob\'s power structure and looks for ways to bring his opponent to justice.', '16833'),
(290, 'The Aftermath', 'Historical drama,Romance,', 'In 1946 a British colonel and his wife share a home with a German widower in Hamburg.', '538', 2019, '2020-10-23T03:55Z', '2020-10-23T05:45Z', '110', 'MV011636060000', '15592224', '2019-03-15', 'en', 'In 1946 Rachael Morgan arrives in the ruins of Hamburg to be reunited with her husband, Lewis, who is a British colonel charged with rebuilding the shattered city. As they set off for their new home, Rachael is stunned to discover that Lewis has made an unexpected decision: They will be sharing the grand house with its previous owners, a German widower and his troubled daughter. In this charged atmosphere, enmity and grief give way to passion and betrayal.', '25621'),
(291, 'Curly Sue', 'Comedy drama,', 'A con man (James Belushi) and an orphan tyke (Alisan Porter) steal a lawyer\'s (Kelly Lynch) heart.', '584', 1991, '2020-10-23T03:55Z', '2020-10-23T05:39Z', '104', 'MV000341360000', '13523', '1991-10-25', 'en', 'Bill (James Belushi) is a penniless drifter who scams strangers out of just enough money to feed himself and his partner in crime, an orphan girl known as Curly Sue (Alisan Porter). Bill and Curly Sue target Grey (Kelly Lynch), a yuppie lawyer, but their con takes an unexpected turn when the successful woman begins to like the ramshackle duo. She decides to take the girl in and falls in love with Bill, but there\'s one problem -- Grey\'s jealous, conniving boyfriend, Walker (John Getz).', '19635'),
(292, 'Shaft', 'Action,', 'A detective (Samuel L. Jackson) and his partner (Vanessa L. Williams) track a sociopath.', '552', 2000, '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '2020-10-23T05:45Z', '105', 'MV000925000000', '25675', '2000-06-16', 'en', 'Crooked cops on the take -- small-time drug lords -- sleazy informers and sadistic rich kids ready to kill --- for police detective John Shaft, its just another night in the underbelly of New York City, another shift facing down cops and criminals who want him dead and a legal system that thrives on money, not justice.', '11116'),
(293, 'Silverado', 'Western,', 'Old West drifters (Kevin Kline, Scott Glenn, Kevin Costner) shoot it out with sheriff, clan.', '609', 1985, '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '2020-10-23T06:17Z', '137', 'MV000187360000', '8716', '1985-07-10', 'en', 'Rambling man Emmett (Scott Glenn) assembles a group of misfit cowboys (Kevin Costner), (Kevin Kline, Danny Glover). After helping a group of settlers track down a pack of thieves, Emmett and his men descend on the troubled town of Silverado to seek their fortunes. Soon after arriving, they discover that the town has fallen into the grasp of greedy rancher Ethan McKendrick (Ray Baker) and corrupt Sheriff Cobb (Brian Dennehy) with whom many of Emmett\'s men have unfinished business.', '17125'),
(294, 'Crimson Peak', 'Horror,Mystery,Romance,', 'A new bride investigates ghostly visions at a remote gothic mansion that holds dark secrets.', '535', 2015, '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '120', 'MV007631040000', '11806131', '2015-10-16', 'en', 'After marrying the charming and seductive Sir Thomas Sharpe, young Edith (Mia Wasikowska) finds herself swept away to his remote gothic mansion in the English hills. Also living there is Lady Lucille, Thomas\' alluring sister and protector of her family\'s dark secrets. Able to communicate with the dead, Edith tries to decipher the mystery behind the ghostly visions that haunt her new home. As she comes closer to the truth, Edith may learn that true monsters are made of flesh and blood.', '25622'),
(295, 'xXx: Return of Xander Cage', 'Action,Adventure,Thriller,', 'Daredevil operative Xander Cage battles four criminals who control the world\'s military satellites.', '068', 2017, '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '120', 'MV008573590000', '12604116', '2017-01-20', 'en', 'After coming out of self-imposed exile, daredevil operative Xander Cage (Vin Diesel) must race against time to recover a sinister weapon known as Pandora\'s Box, a device that controls every military satellite in the world. Recruiting a new group of thrill-seeking cohorts, Xander finds himself entangled in a deadly conspiracy that points to collusion at the highest levels of government.', '14321'),
(296, 'xXx: Return of Xander Cage', 'Action,Adventure,Thriller,', 'Daredevil operative Xander Cage battles four criminals who control the world\'s military satellites.', '108', 2017, '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '120', 'MV008573590000', '12604116', '2017-01-20', 'en', 'After coming out of self-imposed exile, daredevil operative Xander Cage (Vin Diesel) must race against time to recover a sinister weapon known as Pandora\'s Box, a device that controls every military satellite in the world. Recruiting a new group of thrill-seeking cohorts, Xander finds himself entangled in a deadly conspiracy that points to collusion at the highest levels of government.', '14321'),
(297, 'Tim Burton\'s Corpse Bride', 'Fantasy,Animated,Children,', 'A man (Johnny Depp) weds a dead woman (Helena Bonham Carter) and sees the underworld.', '037', 2005, '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '120', 'MV001621000000', '36328', '2005-09-07', 'en', 'Victor (Johnny Depp) and Victoria\'s (Emily Watson) families have arranged their marriage. Though they like each other, Victor is nervous about the ceremony. While he\'s in a forest practicing his lines for the wedding, a tree branch becomes a hand that drags him to the land of the dead. It belongs to Emily, who was murdered after eloping with her love and wants to marry Victor. Victor must get back aboveground before Victoria marries the villainous Barkis Bittern (Richard E. Grant).', '10093'),
(298, 'Tim Burton\'s Corpse Bride', 'Fantasy,Animated,Children,', 'A man (Johnny Depp) weds a dead woman (Helena Bonham Carter) and sees the underworld.', '122', 2005, '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '120', 'MV001621000000', '36328', '2005-09-07', 'en', 'Victor (Johnny Depp) and Victoria\'s (Emily Watson) families have arranged their marriage. Though they like each other, Victor is nervous about the ceremony. While he\'s in a forest practicing his lines for the wedding, a tree branch becomes a hand that drags him to the land of the dead. It belongs to Emily, who was murdered after eloping with her love and wants to marry Victor. Victor must get back aboveground before Victoria marries the villainous Barkis Bittern (Richard E. Grant).', '10093'),
(299, 'Aquaman', 'Action,Adventure,Fantasy,', 'Aquaman must retrieve the legendary Trident of Atlan to save Atlantis from his power-hungry brother.', '518', 2018, '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '2020-10-23T06:30Z', '150', 'MV009632610000', '13579498', '2018-12-21', 'en', 'Once home to the most advanced civilization on Earth, the city of Atlantis is now an underwater kingdom ruled by the power-hungry King Orm. With a vast army at his disposal, Orm plans to conquer the remaining oceanic people -- and then the surface world. Standing in his way is Arthur, Orm\'s half-human, half-Atlantean brother and true heir to the throne. With help from royal counselor Vulko, Arthur must retrieve the legendary Trident of Atlan and embrace his destiny as protector of the deep sea.', '10244'),
(300, 'Pyar Ki Takkar', 'Drama,', 'Vijayakanth falls in love with Shobana but she denies his love for reasons unknown at the time.', '1532', 1989, '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '2020-10-23T07:00Z', '180', 'MV004823770000', '9936247', '1989', 'hi', 'Vijayakanth, the innocent son of M N Nambiar, falls in love with the local MLA\'s daughter, Shobana. Vijayakanth\'s life changes forever when she denies his love for reasons unknown at the time.', '52285'),
