(308, 'The Watcher', 'Thriller,', 'An FBI agent (James Spader) comes out of hiding to catch a serial killer (Keanu Reeves).', '533', 2000, '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '2020-10-23T05:40Z', '100', 'MV000969820000', '26173', '2000-09-08', 'en', '\"The Watcher\" is an exciting psychological thriller that takes a unique look into the minds of both a serial killer and the man who must, reluctantly, pursue him. In an almost Hitchcockian way, the film quickly introduces us to the killer, David Allen Griffin, played by Keanu Reeves, who for many years, preyed on lonely young women in the Los Angeles area. The story is set up to create a taut cat-and-mouse game between Griffin and FBI agent Joel Campbell.', '18433'),
(309, 'The Babysitter\'s Revenge', 'Thriller,', 'A teenager plots revenge against the girl who caused a humiliating scandal for her family.', '076', 2020, '2020-10-23T04:00Z', '2020-10-23T06:00Z', '120', 'MV013619750000', '17760347', '2020', 'en', 'When a teenager discovers that the neighborhood gossip may be to blame for a humiliating scandal, she is determined to exact revenge, even if it means ruining other lives.', '18480'),
